crucial%20to%20his%202024%20reelection%20campaign.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20long%20been%20a%20skeptic%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20and%20during%20his%20administration%2C%20he%20pushed%20heavily%20for%20expanded%20drilling%20on%20public%20lands%20and%20in%20federal%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20the%20former%20president%20touts%20his%20past%20record%20and%20campaigns%20for%20the%202024%20GOP%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20he%20is%20wooing%20oil%20and%20gas%20barons%20to%20line%20up%20behind%20his%20candidacy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2F11%2F10%2Ftrump-oil-gas-donors-climate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20the%20nation's%20top%20energy%20executives%20may%20have%20already%20been%20inclined%20to%20support%20Trump%2C%20attracted%20to%20the%20former%20president's%20support%20for%20increased%20oil%20production%20and%20his%20distaste%20for%20environmental%20regulations%20favored%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20leaders%20had%20also%20been%20entertaining%20entreaties%20from%20other%20Republican%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarold%20Hamm%2C%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20and%20chairman%20of%20Continental%20Resources%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20told%20Trump%20during%20a%20phone%20conversation%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20he%20should%20end%20his%20presidential%20bid%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fc93982ee-4387-4c95-9bb1-a7cd3b89bbe7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20The%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Hamm%20said%20there%20was%20too%20much%20%26quot%3Bchaos%26quot%3B%20surrounding%20Trump%2C%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20donate%20to%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20of%20Florida%20and%20former%20Gov.%20Nikki%20Haley%20of%20South%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20last%20month%2C%20Hamm%20visited%20Trump's%20Mar-a-Lago%20club%20with%20a%20%24200%2C000%20check%20for%20a%20super%20PAC%20supporting%20the%20former%20president%20and%20went%20to%20a%20private%20meeting%20and%20a%20fundraiser%20with%20him%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20his%20campaign%20have%20made%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20create%20an%20air%20of%20inevitability%20surrounding%20his%20third%20White%20House%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%202024%20is%20actively%20courting%20the%20right%20people%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20them%20on%20board%2C%20but%20specifically%20the%20oil%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Canary%20LLC%20chief%20executive%20Dan%20Eberhart%20told%20The%20Post.%20%26quot%3BThey%20know%20who%20they%20need%20to%20get%20on%20the%20Trump%20train%2C%20and%20they're%20doing%20what%20they%20need%20to%20do%20to%20get%20those%20folks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEberhart%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDanKEberhart%2Fstatus%2F1716830093082079297%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrown%20his%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20behind%20DeSantis'%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20November%2C%20about%20400%20affluent%20Texas%20donors%2C%20including%20individuals%20tied%20to%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20industry%2C%20came%20to%20the%20complex%20of%20telecommunications%20billionaire%20Kenny%20Troutt%20for%20a%20Trump%20event.%20Some%20of%20the%20attendees%20paid%20upwards%20of%20%2423%2C200%20to%20take%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20former%20president%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pumpjack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654fda9836d588dc55cf0c39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223038%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20pumpjack%20dips%20its%20head%20to%20extract%20oil%20in%20a%20basin%20north%20of%20Helper%2C%20Utah.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FRick%20Bowmer%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20runs%20on%20his%20administration's%20record%20%E2%80%94%20he%20severely%20weakened%20the%20environmental%20rules%20put%20into%20place%20by%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20and%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pulling-us-out-paris-climate-agreement-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20climate%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-takes-immediate-action-climate-rejoins-paris-accord-keystone-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erejoined%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20accord%20upon%20taking%20office)%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20looking%20to%20remind%20the%20group%20of%20his%20conservative%20bonafides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20in%20canceling%20the%20Keystone%20XL%20oil%20pipeline%20and%20also%20canceling%20oil%20and%20gas%20leases%20in%20the%20Arctic%20National%20Wildlife%20Refuge%20(ANWR)%20in%20northeastern%20Alaska%2C%20has%20staked%20out%20pro-environmental%20positions%20that%20Trump%20says%20have%20weakened%20the%20United%20States%20on%20energy%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20praised%20Biden's%20commitment%20to%20pushing%20the%20production%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20expanding%20solar%20energy%2C%20both%20issues%20that%20Trump%20has%20railed%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Trump%20questioning%20the%20efficiency%20of%20batteries%20in%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20he%20has%20spoken%20out%20against%20wind%20turbines%20and%20has%20advocated%20for%20more%20drilling%20in%20the%20continental%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Texas%20event%2C%20the%20former%20president%20pledged%20to%20reverse%20Biden's%20Keystone%20XL%20decision%20and%20restore%20canceled%20oil%20and%20gas%20leases%20in%20ANWR%2C%20while%20also%20slamming%20electric%20vehicle%20mandates%20and%20vowing%20to%20fight%20against%20progressive-led%20efforts%20like%20the%20Green%20New%20Deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20was%20good%20on%20energy%2C%20and%20I%20think%20energy%20policy%20under%20Trump%20would%20be%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Eberhart%2C%20the%20DeSantis%20supporter%2C%20told%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extent%20of%20Trump's%20pitches%20to%20energy%20executives%20is%20not%20a%20shock%20to%20environmental%20groups%2C%20as%20they%20battled%20with%20the%20administration%20over%20regulations%20throughout%20his%20entire%20time%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20aren't%20enough%20hours%20in%20the%20day%20to%20discuss%20how%20horrific%20the%20former%20president's%20record%20is%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20clean%20air%2C%20clean%20water%2C%20and%20public%20lands%2C%26quot%3B%20League%20of%20Conservation%20Voters%20senior%20vice%20president%20for%20government%20affairs%20Tiernan%20Sittenfeld%20told%20The%20Post.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20fact%20that%20Big%20Oil%20is%20coming%20back%20to%20him%20is%20perhaps%20not%20surprising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Post%2C%20Trump%20spokesman%20Steven%20Cheung%20slammed%20the%20Biden%20administration%20over%20its%20energy%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20President%20Trump%20has%20said%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20multiple%20times%2C%20we%20need%20to%20increase%20energy%20production%20in%20order%20to%20help%20supercharge%20the%20economy%20and%20ease%20inflation%20caused%20by%20Biden's%20disastrous%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-oil-gas-industry-political-donations-environment-drilling-2024-campaign-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699733853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654fdb6a36d588dc55cf0c4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-oil-gas-industry-political-donations-environment-drilling-2024-campaign