ad%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20made%20a%20strong%20outreach%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20particularly%20the%20Madigas%2C%20who%20make%20up%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20community%20in%20the%20state.%20PM%20Modi%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20empower%20Madigas%20and%20look%20into%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20three-decade-old%20demand%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20is%20significant%20because%20the%20Madigas%20can%20decisively%20influence%20the%20outcome%20in%2020-25%20seats%20in%20the%20119-strong%20Telangana%20assembly%2C%20where%20the%20number%20needed%20for%20a%20majority%20is%2060.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20speaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Secunderabad%20organised%20by%20the%20Madiga%20Reservation%20Porata%20Samithi%2C%20whose%20founder%2C%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga%2C%20broke%20down%20when%20PM%20Modi%20said%20he%20supports%20him%20and%20his%20cause.%20The%20PM%20was%20seen%20consoling%20the%20leader%2C%20who%20later%20announced%20his%20organisation's%20support%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20being%20anti-Dalit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommittee%20To%20Be%20Formed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20ending%20this%20injustice%20at%20the%20earliest.%20It%20is%20our%20promise%20that%20we%20will%20soon%20constitute%20a%20committee%20that%20will%20adopt%20all%20possible%20ways%20to%20empower%20you%20(the%20Madiga%20community).%20You%20and%20we%20also%20know%20that%20a%20big%20legal%20process%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%20consider%20your%20struggle%20to%20be%20just%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20ensure%20justice.%20It%20is%20the%20top%20priority%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20you%20get%20justice%20in%20court%20also.%20With%20full%20strength%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20will%20stand%20in%20favour%20of%20justice%20as%20your%20colleague%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20equitable%20welfare%20and%20social%20justice%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20this%20point%20that%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga%20got%20emotional%20and%20broke%20into%20tears%2C%20and%20the%20PM%20was%20later%20seen%20consoling%20him%2C%20holding%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday's%20public%20meeting%20will%20remain%20etched%20in%20my%20memory.%20The%20affection%20from%20my%20Dalit%20sisters%20and%20brothers%2C%20my%20Madiga%20sisters%20and%20brothers%20is%20tremendous.%20I%20salute%20my%20brother%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga%20for%20his%20efforts%20towards%20empowering%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThank%20you%20Hyderabad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnToday's%20public%20meeting%20will%20remain%20etched%20in%20my%20memory.%20The%20affection%20from%20my%20Dalit%20sisters%20and%20brothers%2C%20my%20Madiga%20sisters%20and%20brothers%20is%20tremendous.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20salute%20my%20brother%20Manda%20Krishna%20Madiga%20for%20his%20efforts%20towards%20empowering%20people.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSome%20glimpses%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOLrXlkIOEK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOLrXlkIOEK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1723344129185452448%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C