son%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefense%20Blog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20military%20blog%20run%20by%20a%20former%20Ukrainian%20defense%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20pilots%20are%20already%20undergoing%20air%20training%20with%20an%20instructor%20on%20combat%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20Ignat%20said%20during%20a%20nationally%20televised%20broadcast%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BSo%20everything%20is%20going%20according%20to%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20sought%20F-16s%20for%20its%20arsenal%20of%20fighter%20jets%20since%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Russia's%20invasion.%20John%20Baum%2C%20a%20retired%20US%20Air%20Force%20lieutenant%20colonel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-f-16s-getting-capable-missiles-variety-missions-russian-jets-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20American-made%20F-16%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20capable%26quot%3B%20dogfighting%20jets%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20more%20technologically%20advanced%20jets%2C%20like%20the%20MiG-31%20and%20Su-25%2C%20can%20outmaneuver%20Ukraine's%20Soviet-era%20MiG-29%20and%20Su-27%20using%20advanced%20equipment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-wants-f-16s-soviet-fighter-jets-dont-cut-it-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ukraine%20needs%20the%20modern%20F-16%20to%20better%20compete%2C%20it%20also%20needs%20them%20because%20it's%20proving%20difficult%20to%20repair%20its%20current%20fleet%20of%20fighter%20jets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrynn%20Tannehill%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20and%20former%20US%20Navy%20pilot%2C%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20having%20trouble%20replacing%20parts%20on%20its%20Soviet-made%20jets%20because%20those%20parts%20are%20largely%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20sm