erved%20mental%20health%20need.%20Dr%20Westheimer%20is%20aiming%20to%20help%20New%20Yorkers%20with%20social%20isolation%2C%20which%20is%20associated%20with%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20issues%20such%20as%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20depression%20and%20premature%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20New%20York%20works%20to%20fight%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%2C%20some%20help%20from%20honorary%20Ambassador%20Ruth%20Westheimer%20may%20be%20just%20what%20the%20doctor%20ordered%2C%26quot%3B%20Governor%20Hochul%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.ny.gov%2Fnews%2Fgovernor-hochul-appoints-dr-ruth-westheimer-new-york-states-honorary-ambassador-loneliness%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BStudies%20show%20individuals%20experiencing%20loneliness%20had%20a%2032%20percent%20higher%20risk%20of%20dying%20early%20and%20we%20need%20leaders%20like%20Dr.%20Ruth%20to%20help%20address%20this%20critical%20component%20of%20our%20mental%20health%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20press%20note%2C%20Dr%20Westheimer%20is%20a%20survivor%20orphaned%20by%20the%20Holocaust.%20She%20rose%20to%20prominence%20as%20a%20sex%20therapist%20and%20syndicated%20talk%20show%20host%20on%20both%20radio%20and%20television%20during%20the%201980s%20and%201990s.%20It%20was%20last%20year%2C%20the%2095-year-old%20suggested%20the%20idea%20of%20becoming%20an%20'ambassador'%20for%20the%20state%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20provide%20fellow%20New%20Yorkers%20will%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20address%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%2C%20especially%20amid%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHallelujah!%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Westheimer%20said%20in%20a%20news%20release.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20honored%20and%20promised%20the%20Governor%20that%20I%20will%20work%20day%20and%20night%20to%20help%20New%20Yorkers%20feel%20less%20lonely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeet-mika-the-worlds-first-ever-ai-humanoid-robot-ceo-4567460%5C%22%3EMeet%20'Mika'%2C%20The%20World's%20First%20Ever%20AI%20Humanoid%20Robot%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoneliness%20is%20defined%20as%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20alone%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20social%20contact%2C%20while%20social%20isolation%20refers%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20social%20connections%2C%20as%20per%20the%20press%20release.%20More%20than%20a%20third%20of%20adults%2045%20or%20older%20experience%20loneliness%2C%20while%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20adults%2065%20and%20older%20are%20considered%20socially%20isolated%2C%20a%20study%20by%20the%20National%20Academies%20of%20Science%2C%20Engineering%20and%20Medicine%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20under%20Ms%20Hochul's%20leadership%2C%20New%20York%20is%20working%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bage-friendly%20communities%20and%20build%20a%20more%20robust%20system%20of%20mental%20health%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20news%20release.%20Last%20year%2C%20Governor%20Hochul%20also%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20create%20the%20state's%20first-ever%20Master%20Plan%20for%20Aging%20to%20ensure%20older%20New%20Yorkers%20can%20live%20healthy%2C%20fulfilling%20lives%20while%20ageing%20with%20dignity%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Dr%20Westheimer's%20honorary%20appointment%20underlines%20Ms%20Hochul's%20recent%20emphasis%20on%20ageing%20and%20social%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699721160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2eodp2do_dr-ruth-westheimer_625x300_11_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-york-appoints-sex-therapist-dr-ruth-westheimer-as-states-1st-loneliness-ambassador-4567555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Ruth%20Westheimer%2C%20a%20well-known%20media%20figure%20and%20sex%20therapist%2C%20