20pond%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Maui%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20has%20become%20a%20tourist%20destination%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pond%20recently%20turned%20a%20bright%20pink%20color.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20hypothesize%20a%20draught%20may%20be%20causing%20this%20change%2C%20although%20they%20can't%20say%20for%20sure%20yet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETourists%20have%20been%20flocking%20to%20a%20bright%20pink%20pond%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Maui%2C%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pond%2C%20called%20Ke%C4%81lia%20Pond%2C%20has%20been%20monitored%20by%20the%20Ke%C4%81lia%20Pond%20National%20Wildlife%20Refuge%20since%20October%2030%2C%20when%20its%20color%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20exact%20reason%20for%20this%20change%2C%20but%20they%20hypothesize%20a%20drought%20may%20be%20to%20blame%20and%20are%20warning%20against%20drinking%20the%20water%20or%20swimming%20in%20it%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fws.gov%2Frefuge%2Fkealia-pond%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drought%20has%20likely%20caused%20the%20salt%20levels%20in%20the%20water%20to%20grow%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20halobacteria%20organisms%2C%20causing%20the%20pink%20hue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalobacteria%20are%20%26quot%3Bsalt-loving%20organisms%20found%20in%20high%20salinity%20water%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service.%20The%20salinity%20in%20the%20pond%20is%20currently%20twice%20that%20of%20seawater.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20Nov.%208%2C%202023%2C%20photo%20provided%20by%20Leslie%20Diamond%20shows%20the%20pond%20at%20the%20Kealia%20Pond%20National%20Wildlife%20Refuge%20on%20Maui%2C%20Hawaii.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654fa17c36d588dc55cf07e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ke%C4%81lia%20Pond%20turned%20pink%20on%20October%2030%2C%202023.%20This%20picture%20was%20taken%20on%20November%208.%3Cp%3ELeslie%20Diamond%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pond%20has%20experienced%20drought%20and%20periods%20of%20high%20salinity%20in%20the%20past%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20it%20has%20turned%20pink%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fhawaii-maui-pink-pond-drought-6004cf6ab89d2d72cb54a631e8f7b768%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAP%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBret%20Wolfe%2C%20the%20refuge%20manager%2C%20told%20the%20AP%20that%20he's%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20tourist%20visits%20since%20the%20pink%20pond%20first%20appeared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20prefer%20that%20they%20come%20to%20hear%20about%20our%20mission%20conserving%20native%20and%20endangered%20waterbirds%20and%20our%20wetland%20restorations.%20But%20no%2C%20they're%20here%20to%20see%20the%20pink%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20AP.%20%26quot%3BIf%20that's%20what%20gets%20them%20there%2C%20it's%20OK.%20It%20is%20neat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pond%20is%20home%20to%20two%20endangered%20species%20of%20birds%2C%C2%A0the%20%C2%A0ae'o%C2%A0(Hawaiian%20stilt)%20and%20'alae%C2%A0ke'oke'o%C2%A0(Hawaiian%20coot)%2C%20and%20provides%20nesting%2C%20feeding%2C%20and%20resting%20habitat%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourists-bright-pink-pond-hawaii-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699720737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654f9f39385143459e8bb305%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourists-bright-pink-pond-hawaii-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bright%20pink%20pond%20in%20Maui%2C%20Hawaii%