82%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20J.D.%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20underlined%20how%20many%20Republicans%20will%20not%20simply%20abandon%20the%20issue%20amid%20the%20current%20struggles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20up%20on%20the%20unborn%20is%20not%20an%20option.%20It's%20politically%20dumb%20and%20morally%20repugnant%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJDVance1%2Fstatus%2F1722311695140298978%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EVance%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20own%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20why%20we%20lost%20this%20battle%20so%20we%20can%20win%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20plugged%20into%20the%20push%20against%20the%20amendment%2C%20cautioned%20that%20his%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20more%20to%20work%20on%20its%20appeal%20to%20voters%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BW%5De%20have%20to%20recognize%20how%20much%20voters%20mistrust%20us%20(meaning%20elected%20Republicans)%20on%20this%20issue.%20Having%20an%20unplanned%20pregnancy%20is%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBest%20case%2C%20you're%20looking%20at%20social%20scorn%20and%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20of%20unexpected%20medical%20bills.%20We%20need%20people%20to%20see%20us%20as%20the%20pro-life%20party%2C%20not%20just%20the%20anti-abortion%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESome%20Republicans%20just%20want%20to%20ignore%20voters.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20such%20an%20appeal%20may%20not%20be%20easy.%20As%20Vance%20described%2C%20many%20Republicans%20abandoned%20their%20decades-long%20commitment%20to%20traditional%20exceptions%20to%20abortion%20bans%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20rape%2C%20incest%2C%20or%20the%20mother's%20health.%20In%20a%20push%20for%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bheartbeat%26quot%3B%20bans%20before%20Roe's%20reversal%2C%20several%20states%20abandoned%20some%20or