y%20and%20its%20unique%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20advanced%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning%20algorithm%2C%20I%20can%20swiftly%20and%20accurately%20make%20data-driven%2C%26quot%3B%20Mika%20said%20in%20a%20Dictador%20company%20video.%20%26quot%3BMy%20decision-making%20process%20relies%20on%20extensive%20data%20analysis%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20company's%20strategic%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20devoid%20of%20personal%20bias%2C%20ensuring%20strategic%20choices%20that%20prioritise%20the%20organisation's%20best%20interest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-will-delete-millions-of-gmail-accounts-next-month-heres-why-4563353%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Will%20Delete%20Millions%20Of%20Gmail%20Accounts%20Next%20Month.%20Here's%20Why%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20a%20%3Cem%3EFox%20Business%3C%2Fem%3E%20reporter%20interviewed%20Mika%20over%20a%20video%20call%2C%20she%20found%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20delay%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20time%20it%20took%20for%20the%20robot%20to%20actually%20respond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hanson%20Robotics%20CEO%20David%20Hanson%2C%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20employing%20Mika%20at%20Dictador%2C%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20%26quot%3Bhumanising%26quot%3B%20AI.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20strongly%20that%20we%20need%20to%20teach%20A.I.%20to%20care%20about%20people%20for%20A.I.%20to%20be%20really%20safe%2C%20to%20be%20really%2C%20really%20good.%20I%20think%20humanizing%20that%20is%20a%20very%20important%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCzEMUmBMOxw%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EDictador%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mika%20has%20been%20hailed%20an%20honorary%20professor.%20The%20female%20humanoid%