ruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20vast%20majority%20of%20tourists%20visiting%20Iceland%20pass%20through%20the%20hot%20springs%20of%20the%20Blue%20Lagoon.%20The%20site%20has%20become%20a%20major%20tourist%20attraction%20for%20the%20country.%20The%20volcanic%20eruption%20threatens%20the%20continuity%20of%20this%20beautiful%20place.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654f659f58cf5fbccb953e6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Blue%20Lagoon%2C%20one%20of%20Iceland's%20top%20touristic%20attractions%2C%20has%20been%20shut%20due%20to%20the%20high%20risk%20of%20a%20volcanic%20eruption%20in%20the%20area.%3Cp%3ERaul%20Moreno%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIceland%20has%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20due%20to%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20a%20volcanic%20eruption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20in%20the%20coastal%20town%20of%20Grindav%C3%ADk%20have%20been%20told%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIceland%20has%20seen%20increased%20eruptions%20since%202021%2C%20a%20possible%20sign%20of%20a%20new%20era%20of%20volcanic%20activity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIceland%20has%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20and%20told%20people%20to%20evacuate%20the%20city%20of%20Grindav%C3%ADk%20in%20the%20southwest%20of%20the%20country%20due%20to%20a%20possible%20volcanic%20eruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20emergency%20level%20of%20civil%20protection%20is%20now%20in%20effect.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20emergency%20evacuation.%20Residents%20of%20Grindav%C3%ADk%20are%20advised%20to%20proceed%20with%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.vedur.is%2Fabout-imo%2Fnews%2Fa-seismic-swarm-started-north-of-grindavik-last-night%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIcelandic%20Met%20Office%3C%2Fa%3E%20(IMO)%20said%20late%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Icelandic%20Civil%20Protection%20Agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freykjanes.almannavarnir.is%2Fen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20immediate%20danger%20imminent%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20evacuation%20is%20primarily%20preventive%20with%20the%20safety%20of%20all%20Grindv%C3%ADkin%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IMO%20added%20that%20since%20midnight%20over%20800%20earthquakes%20had%20been%20detected%20around%20the%20region%20where%20magma%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducation.nationalgeographic.org%2Fresource%2Fmagma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20liquid%20or%20semi-liquid%20rock%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20found%20under%20the%20Earth's%20surface%2C%20was%20accumulating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolcanic%20eruptions%20occur%20when%20magma%20breaks%20through%20and%20onto%20the%20Earth's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20indications%20that%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20magma%20is%20moving%20in%20an%20area%20extending%20from%20Sundhnj%C3%BAkag%C3%ADgum%20in%20the%20north%20towards%20Grindav%C3%ADk%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IMO%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20likelihood%20of%20a%20volcanic%20eruption%20occurring%20in%20the%20near%20future%20is%20deemed%20considerable%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20emergency%2C%20the%20Blue%20Lagoon%2C%20one%20of%20Iceland's%20most%20popular%20tourist%20attractions%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20Grindav%C3%ADk%2C%20was%20closed%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Reykjanes%20Peninsula%2C%20the%20area%20where%20Grindav%C3%ADk%20is%20located%2C%20has%20seen%20volcanic%20eruptions%20as%20often%20as%20every%2012%20months%20since%202021%2C%20with%20the%20latest%20coming%20in%20August%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Icelandic%20tourism%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visiticeland.com%2Feru