%20people%20dead%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20239%20taken%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20subsequent%20aerial%20and%20ground%20offensive%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20people%2C%20also%20mostly%20civilians%20and%20many%20of%20them%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHost%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%26quot%3Bconfirms%20that%20it%20holds%20the%20occupation%20(Israeli)%20authorities%20responsible%20for%20the%20crimes%20committed%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%2C%20the%20Gulf%20kingdom's%20de%20facto%20ruler%2C%20said%20as%20Saturday's%20summit%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20certain%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20guarantee%20security%2C%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%20is%20to%20end%20the%20occupation%2C%20siege%20and%20the%20settlements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Israel's%20actions%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%2C%20on%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20since%20the%20two%20countries%20mended%20ties%20in%20March%2C%20said%20Islamic%20countries%20should%20designate%20the%20Israeli%20army%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20conduct%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%20it%20is%20out%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20blames%20the%20Palestinian%20armed%20group%20for%20the%20high%20death%20count%20accusing%20it%20of%20using%20civilians%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20shields%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20charge%20Hamas%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegional%20divisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arab%20League%20and%20the%20OIC%2C%20a%2057-member%20bloc%20that%20includes%20Iran%2C%20were%20originally%20meant%20to%20meet%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArab%20diplomats%20told%20AFP%20the%20decision%20to%20merge%20the%20meetings%20came%20after%20Arab%20League%20deleg