0that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20a%20shame%20that%20Western%20countries%2C%20which%20always%20talk%20about%20human%20rights%20and%20freedoms%2C%20remain%20silent%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20ongoing%20massacres%20in%20Palestine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20said%20Washington%20had%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20influence%20on%20Israel%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbears%20responsibility%20for%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20political%20solution%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20president%20in%20Riyadh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roster%20of%20attendees%20on%20Saturday%20also%20included%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20al-Sisi%2C%20Qatar's%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al-Thani%20and%20Syrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20who%20was%20welcomed%20back%20into%20the%20Arab%20fold%20this%20year%20after%20an%20extended%20rift%20over%20his%20country's%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi%20is%20the%20first%20Iranian%20president%20to%20visit%20Saudi%20Arabia%20since%20Mahmoud%20Ahmadinejad%20attended%20an%20OIC%20meeting%20in%20the%20kingdom%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20backs%20Hamas%20as%20well%20as%20Lebanon's%20Hezbollah%20and%20Yemen's%20Huthi%20rebels%2C%20placing%20it%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20concerns%20the%20war%20could%20expand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20already%20fuelled%20cross-border%20exchanges%20between%20the%20Israeli%20army%20and%20Hezbollah%2C%20and%20the%20Huthis%20have%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20%26quot%3Bballistic%20missiles%26quot%3B%20the%20rebels%20said%20targeted%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20Saudi%20Arabia%20feels%20vulnerable%20to%20potential%20attacks%20because%20of%20its%20close%20ties%20with%20Washington%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20considering%20normalising%20ties%20with%20Israel%20before%20the%20war%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn