20Hamas%2C%20with%20international%20players%20potentially%20filling%20a%20role%20in%20the%20interim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Authority%20currently%20has%20partial%20administrative%20control%20in%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Blinken%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Palestinian%20president%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20said%20the%20PA%20could%20only%20assume%20power%20in%20Gaza%20if%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20political%20solution%26quot%3B%20is%20found%20for%20the%20decades-old%20Israel-Palestinian%20conflict%20encompassing%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20east%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Wednesday%20Blinken%20again%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3BPalestinian-led%20governance%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20a%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bunified%20with%20the%20West%20Bank%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbbas%2C%2088%2C%20who%20has%20led%20the%20PA%20for%2018%20years%2C%20is%20widely%20unpopular%20and%20has%20been%20powerless%20against%20the%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20Israeli%20settlements%20and%20military%20control%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20annexed%20east%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Little%20hope'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20long%20sought%20to%20sideline%20the%20PA%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20told%20Fox%20News%20his%20country%20does%20not%20plan%20to%20reoccupy%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20occupied%20Gaza%20in%201967%20and%20remained%20there%20until%20completing%20a%20withdrawal%20in%202005%2C%20leaving%20local%20authority%20with%20the%20PA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20seek%20to%20govern%20Gaza.%20We%20don't%20seek%20to%20occupy%20it%2C%20but%20we%20seek%20to%20give%20it%20and%20us%20a%20better%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushed%20on%20his%20plan%20for%20Gaza's%20future%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%20the%20impoverished%20and%20blockaded%20territory%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Bdemilitarised%2C%20deradicalised%20and%20rebuilt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20have%20to%20find%20a%20government%2C%20a%20civilian%20government%20that%20will%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20without%20detailing%20who%20might%20form%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20its%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Hamas%20fighters%20poured%20across%20the%20heavily%20militarised%20border%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20about%201%2C200%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20taking%20around%20240%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVowing%20to%20destroy%20the%20group%2C%20Israel%20retaliated%20with%20bombardment%20and%20a%20ground%20campaign%20that%20the%20Hamas%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20says%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%20including%20thousands%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20any%20actor%20will%20agree%20to%20govern%20Gaza%20in%20these%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hasan%20Khreisheh%2C%20deputy%20speaker%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20which%20has%20not%20met%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Palestinian%2C%20no%20sane%20person%20will%20agree%20to%20return%20to%20Gaza%20on%20an%20American%20or%20Israeli%20tank.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%2C%20the%20International%20Crisis%20Group%20(ICG)%20of%20analysts%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Blittle%20hope%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20already%20deeply%20unpopular%20Palestinian%20Authority%20could%20return%20to%20Gaza%20on%20the%20back%20of%20an%20Israeli%20invasion%20and%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Btreated%20as%20an%20enemy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20one%20knows'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Lebanon-based%20senior%20Hamas%20official%20Osama%20Hamdan%20said%20the%20group%20will%20not%20accept%20a%20puppet%20government%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20people%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20United%20States%20to%20impose%20its%20plans%20to%20create%20an%20administration%20that%20suits%20it%20and%20that%20suits%20the%20occupation%20(Israel)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20Britain%2C%20Israel%20and%20others%20have%20designated%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaleh%20al-Aruri%2C%20the%20group's%20exiled%20deputy%20chief%20of%20political%20affairs%2C%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20future%20of%20Hamas%20cannot%20be%20divorced%20from%20that%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20as%20a%20whole.%20To%20%26quot%3Btalk%20about%20post-Hamas%20is%20to%20talk%20about%20post-Palestine%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20alongside%20Hamas%2C%20vowed%20to%20reject%20any%20imposed%20power%20on%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20an%20international%20force%20were%20to%20be%20deployed%20to%20govern%20Gaza...%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20would%20consider%20it%20an%20occupying%20force%20and%20oppose%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mohammad%20al-Hindi%2C%20the%20group's%20deputy%20secretary-general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20al-Fadi%2C%20a%20political%20and%20international%20relations%20professor%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20believes%20that%20even%20if%20the%20PA%20agreed%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20Gaza%2C%20it%20would%20not%20do%20so%20without%20a%20potential%20agreement%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20this%2C%20he%20told%20AFP%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20would%20%26quot%3Brun%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20new%20civil%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajed%20al-Aruri%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20advocate%20based%20in%20Ramallah%2C%20in%20the%20Israel-occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20said%20everyone%20knows%20how%20the%20latest%20war%20s