0were%20ready%20to%20compromise.%20But%20they%20kept%20hitting%20him%20and%20then%20even%20disrobed%20my%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sapna.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20kept%20screaming%20and%20pleading%20but%20they%20beat%20my%20brother%20to%20death%20in%20front%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESapna%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20men%20also%20threatened%20to%20rape%20her%20if%20she%20complained%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98What%20will%20you%20do%20in%20the%20morning%3F%E2%80%99%20they%20asked%20me.%20%E2%80%98Book%20us%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20Act%3F%20We%20will%20do%20a%20376%20%5BIPC%20section%20for%20rape%5D%20with%20you.%20What%20can%20you%20do%3F%20Your%20FIR%20will%20also%20not%20be%20registered%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20threatened%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sapna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second-year%20BA%20student%2C%20Sapna%20said%20most%20of%20the%20demands%20made%20by%20her%20to%20the%20administration%20following%20the%20incident%20were%20not%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20justice.%20Their%20homes%20were%20not%20demolished.%20The%20main%20accused%2C%20Ankit%20Singh%2C%20was%20not%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%20We%20were%20not%20rehabilitated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mob%20had%20also%20vandalised%20the%20Dalit%20family%E2%80%99s%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20spare%20my%20daily%20utensils%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Munni%20Devi%2C%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20damaged%20portion%20of%20the%20brick%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20450px)%2085vw%2C%20450px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10203107%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-50-50-429-1-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10203107%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-50-50-429-1-768x1024.jpg