%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-is-stuck-and-india-is-stuck-next-to-it%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Is%20Stuck%20and%20India%20Is%20Stuck%20Next%20to%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20negotiated%20joint%20statement%20stated%20that%20the%20ministers%20%E2%80%9Ccondemned%20terrorism%20and%20violent%20extremism%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20terrorist%20proxies%20and%20logistical%2C%20financial%20or%20military%20support%20to%20terrorist%20organisations%2C%20which%20could%20be%20used%20to%20launch%20or%20plan%20terrorist%20attacks%2C%20including%20international%20attacks%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20justice%20for%20the%2026%2F11%20and%20Pathankot%20terror%20attacks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20need%20for%20action%20against%20UN%20proscribed%20terror%20groups%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20as%20Al-Qa%E2%80%99ida%2C%20ISIS%2F%3Cem%3EDaesh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Lashkar-e-Tayyiba%2C%20and%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20without%20any%20explicit%20mention%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ministerial-level%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20India-US%20ministerial%20talks%2C%20highlighting%20the%20differing%20approaches%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20general%20elections%20there%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladeshi%20opposition%20has%20threatened%20to%20boycott%20the%20elections%20if%20a%20caretaker%20government%20is%20not%20established.%20The%20US%20has%20started%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Ftaking-steps-to-impose-visa-restrictions-on-individuals-involved-in-undermining-the-democratic-election-process-in-bangladesh%2F%5C%22%3Eimpose%20visa%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20for%20allegedly%20being%20complicit%20in%20undermining%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20secretary%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20Indi