0pictures%20and%20names%20of%20toppers%20without%20indicating%20the%20length%20of%20the%20course%2C%20the%20fees%20paid%20or%20the%20course%20opted%20to%20lure%20prospective%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20advertisement%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20valid%20and%20not%20deceitful%20when%20it%20does%20not%20mislead%20consumers%20by%20exaggerating%20the%20usefulness%20of%20the%20products%20or%20services%2C%20says%20the%20consumer%20affairs%20ministry.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSG%20was%20found%20making%20false%20claims%20such%20as%20682%20out%20of%20933%20selected%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20students%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20from%20KSG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20DG%20(Investigation)%20CCPA%20was%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20the%20matters%20and%20it%20was%20found%20in%20the%20investigation%20report%20that%20out%20of%20682%2C%20only%20eight%20successful%20candidates%20took%20guidance%20for%20additional%20courses%20and%20that%20too%20in%20previous%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20those%208%2C%20the%20five%20toppers%20only%20took%20mock%20interview%20programmes%20from%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20which%20were%20free%20of%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20being%20lured%20by%20such%20scams%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20red%20flags%20to%20spot%20as%20suggested%20by%20Aakarsh%20Agarwal%2C%20a%20motivational%20speaker%2C%20lawyer%2C%20and%20financial%20guide%20on%20Quora.%20Aakarsh%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20views%20on%20his%20profile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Do%20not%20fall%20for%20unrealistic%20success%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coaching%20centre%20claiming%20a%2099%20percent%20or%20100%20percent%20success%20rate%20is%20a%20big%20red%20flag%20according%20to%20Aakarsh.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20success%20rates%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20the%20difficulty%20level%20of%20the%20exam%20and%20the%20individual%20abilities%20of%20the%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Beware%20of%20fake%20reviews%20and%20testimonials%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkarsh%20says%20that%20if%20there%20are%20too%20many%20good%20reviews%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262120%2Fjharkhand-free-online-classes-zoom-youtube-paathshala-upsc-examinations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20coaching%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20they%20might%20be%20fake.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20try%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20reviews%20by%20checking%20if%20they%20are%20from%20real%20people%20and%20if%20they%20have%20similar%20language%20or%20writing%20styles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Ask%20for%20result%20verification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20asking%20for%20verification%20of%20all%20the%20good%20results%20the%20institute%20is%20claiming.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20their%20students%E2%80%99%20success%2C%20such%20as%20exam%20scores%20or%20certificates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20red%20flag.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20upon%20request%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Check%20for%20accreditation%20or%20certification%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20red%20flag%20that%20he%20suggests%20that%20everyone%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20is%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20accredited%20or%20certified%20by%20a%20recognised%20organisation%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20are%20not%20meeting%20certain%20standards%20or%20regulations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Lack%20of%20transparency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20transparent%20about%20its%20teaching%20methods%2C%20course%20materials%2C%20or%20success%20rates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20prospective%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakarsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Searching%20for%20the%20best%20UPSC%20coaching%20institute%3F%20The%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20has%20just%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%20for%20misleading%20ads%20with%20IAS%20toppers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334054%2Fccpa-fines-khan-study-group-how-to-choose-upsc-coaching-centre-in-delhi-ias-toppers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindustan%20Copper%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20jumps%20two-fold%20at%20Rs%2061%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-10%2F30%2Ffull%2F1667152728-8417.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fhindustan-copper-q2-results-ne