vegas-hotel-workers-strike_n_654baa16e4b0069a0437dacb%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%20Know%20What%20Parents%20Feel%E2%80%99%3A%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20Loving%20Home%20Offers%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Safety%20to%20Kids%20With%20Disabilities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sugwekars%2C%20a%20couple%20based%20in%20Thane%2C%20believe%20that%20their%20son%20Akshay%20was%20born%20to%20make%20them%20realise%20their%20purpose%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20to%20serve%20other%20children%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317722%2Fmumbai-entrepreneurs-start-marketplace-for-ngo-products-jhappi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisabilities%20like%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20Sujata%20and%20Ravindra%20Sugwekar%20have%20been%20doing%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20through%20their%20shelter%20home%2C%20%E2%80%98Sangopita%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20these%20two%20extraordinary%20individuals%20begins%20in%20a%20way%20in%201997%20in%20a%20Badlapur%20hospital.%20Pregnant%20with%20twins%2C%20Sujata%20went%20into%20labour%20in%20just%206.5%20months.%20They%20unfortunately%20lost%20one%20baby%20at%20birth%2C%20while%20the%20other%2C%20Akshay%2C%20was%20fighting%20for%20his%20life.%20Since%20they%20needed%20a%20hospital%20with%20an%20NICU%20(Neonatal%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit)%20and%20good%20paediatric%20services%2C%20they%20moved%20him%20to%20KEM%20hospital%20in%20Parel%2C%20where%20he%20was%20kept%20in%20an%20incubator%20for%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshay%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20a%20neurological%20condition%20that%20affects%20movement%20and%20muscle%20coordination.%20He%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20physiotherapy%20daily%20since%20then.%20As%20Ravindra%20was%20working%20in%20a%20bank%2C%20Sujata%20took%20on%20this%20responsibility.%20She%20would%20carry%20her%20month-old%20baby%20%E2%80%94%20who%20hardly%20weighed